{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-298-selective-amnesia","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 298: Zaboravljanje izbora","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Larry i Robin igraju igru pamćenja koja uključuje niz nasumičnih brojeva između 1 i 10, koji se izgovaraju jedan po drugom. Svaki igrač može zapamtiti do pet prethodnih brojeva. Kada je broj koji se izgovara u memoriji igrača, taj igrač dobija jednu poen. Ako nije tu, igrač dodaje taj broj u svoju memoriju, uklanjajući drugi broj ako je njegova memorija puna.</p>\n<p>Svi igrači počinju sa praznom memorijom. Svi dodaju nove brojeve koje su propustili u svoje memorije, ali koriste različite strategije da odluče koji broj treba ukloniti: strategija Laryja je da ukloni broj koji nije spomenut najduže vreme. Strategija Robina je da ukloni broj koji je najduže bio u memoriji.</p>\n<p>Igra primera:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Smena</th>\n<th>Pozvani broj</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Memorija Laryja</th>\n<th>Bodovi Laryja</th>\n<th>Memorija Robina</th>\n<th>Bodovi Robina</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1,2</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1,2,4</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4,6</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1,2,4,6</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4,6</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1,2,4,6</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4,6,8</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1,2,4,6,8</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,4,6,8,10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2,4,6,8,10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,6,8,10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2,4,6,8,10</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4,8,10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2,4,6,8,10</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td align=\"right\">1,2,4,8,10</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>1,4,6,8,10</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Predstavljajući rezultate Larija sa $L$ i rezultate Robina sa $R$, koja je očekivana vrednost $|L - R|$ nakon 50 pokušaja? Navedite svoj odgovor zaokružen na osam decimalnih mesta koristeći format x.xxxxxxxx.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4971000cf542c50ffa9","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301950,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-298-selective-amnesia"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function selectiveAmnesia() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nselectiveAmnesia();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>selectiveAmnesia()</code> treba da vrati <code>1.76882294</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(selectiveAmnesia(), 1.76882294);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-298-selective-amnesia","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-2